title: A really good app!!!
text: Ok, don’t get me wrong, but l love this app. It’s awesome!! You can create shorts, lives, and long form videos! But, the thing is, everyone knows there’s adds everywhere. I just don’t think that there should be anything on YouTube shorts. Like, I keep scrolling, and I come across the same adds everyday! It’s gotten to the point where it’s just annoying. Sometimes, I even have the app. I’m not saying that YouTube is annoying, it’s just an opinion. Also, I know I do like some of the adds, and I use some of them. But, sometimes it’s just too annoying. I also think it’s really cool that you can post about pretty much everything! I really think that you should download this app. Anyway, have a great day/night!! 😊😊
